description:
As per initial reports the crash of Air India Flight 171 has resulted in more than 250 people losing their lives - some reports claiming upto 300 dead - due the flight crashing into BJ Medical College. What caused this terrible accident? Was it Boeing at fault again or a small pilot error that took place during the most sensitive part of the flight? Many question will have to be honestly answered in the coming days.
